data.title: Connecting people by driving innovation - About
data.meta_description: TELUS Ventures is focused on enabling an ecosystem of innovation by partnering with disruptive, market-transforming companies in early-to-late stage development.
data.text: Acquired by IBM/Tivoli (NYSE: IBM) Intelliden Corporation's intelligent networking software solutions enable enterprises, service providers and government organizations to automate network and device configuration, reduce network costs, improve network security and accelerate service management by linking network and IT resources to business objectives. The company was acquired by IBM/Tivoli in February 2010.
